	   <tr><td colspan=2>I was wandering around in there and saw this same mob... a Lugglad Assassin, but he had a funky knife in his hand... (serrated dagger with green gem model) and so I found my way to a spot where I could single pull him...&nbsp;&nbsp;I got him over to me with no adds just fine but he started pummeling me for double 140's quite fast, so I had to feign him off.<br><br>I waited until the aggro chilled out and then began seeking a healing partner for this critter and eventually found a 56 or 57 druid willing to help drop him.  With him spending all his full bar of mana on heals plus a DS we were able to get him... but barely.<br><br>He dropped a Pure INT caster olny knife...  stats were:<br><br>11/18 <br>5int<br>5cha<br>5dex?<br>20hp<br>25mana<br><br>as I remember it...  I forget the name.<br><br>Peace.<br><br>oh, PS - this was in the chamber at the end of the first tunnel going off to the right after entering the secret luggald caves.<br><br><br>_______________________<br>Baron Ashremm Daystar<br>57 Monk of Luclin<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
